            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-6285.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from G. H. K. Thwaites, 22 July 1868</ref> and n. 3.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-6285.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from G. H. K. Thwaites, 22 July 1868</ref> and enclosure. CD’s letter of 2 September 1868 to <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1889.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Samuel Owen Glenie</ref> has not been found, but see the <ref target="./DCP-LETT-6482.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from S. O. Glenie, 27 November 1868</ref>.</note>
